00:02:59,290 --> 00:03:00,420
Alice!

15
00:03:09,090 --> 00:03:12,970
Pořád pro tebe tělo nic neznamená?

16
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:22,560
Alice...

17
00:03:41,330 --> 00:03:42,630
Ne!

18
